nodes.text: The Coruscant Holo Net: Ru-ful War

The Coruscant Holo Net: Ru-ful War was an in-universe issue of The Coruscant Holo Net that was published in Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.52. It was later reprinted in Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 21. It extrapolated on events featured in the comic story Paradise Lost.
